pochi: extensible Java birthmark toolkit 2.3.24 API

モジュール 
モジュール 説明
jp.cafebabe.birthmarks
This module jp.cafebabe.birthmarks represents APIs for birthmarking.
jp.cafebabe.kunai
The module jp.cafebabe.kunai handles the reading and writing the class files.
jp.cafebabe.pochi
The module jp.cafebabe.pochi contains the implementation classes of the APIs defined in the module jp.cafebabe.birthmarks.
jp.cafebabe.pochicmd
This module is for wrapping the groovy command (groovy and groovysh).
